Name: Lesser Bifra Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Basic Bifra Rune, Level 1 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes the bridge between realms, a path from the divine to mortalkind, allowing those who channel it to tap into the power of translocation.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACESpatial BondSPACEAs a bonus action, you choose one willing creature within DISTANCE30-60DISTANCE feet of you and instantaneously swap locations with them. This does not provoke attacks of opportunity.SPACESPACEYou may invoke this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 2 runic attunement slots. Requires Wisdom 14 or greater to attune for a creature who did not craft the rune.
